*&quot;Hiker&#x27;s Philosophy&quot; chapter of &quot;Footpath in the Wilderness&quot; 1941. (with W. Storrs, James P. Taylor, Charles E. Crane, Wallace Cady, George D. Aiken, Herbert Wheaton Congdon, Robert C. Anderson, and Richard L. Brown)
